Requirements:
CUDA: https://developer.nvidia.com/cuda-12-3-0-download-archive
cublas: https://developer.nvidia.com/cublas
SciPy: https://scipy.org/install/
NumPy: https://numpy.org/install/
matplotlib: https://matplotlib.org/stable/install/index.html

Installation:
1. Check lib/Makefile, src/Makefile and script/Run_GPU_2DES, and modify PATHs accordingly.
2. cd lib; make clean; make
3. cd ../src ; make clean ; make
